    public static enum SessionEndedRequest.Reason
extends java.lang.Enum<SessionEndedRequest.Reason>
    This enum lists the reasons why a Speechlet session ended when not initiated by the Speechlet itself.
    See Also:
    SessionEndedRequest.getReason()

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      ERROR

      EXCEEDED_MAX_REPROMPTS
      The Alexa skill has not received a valid response within the maximum allowed number of re-prompts.

      The user explicitly exited the Speechlet.
